msgctxt "secretf/07_town1"
msgid ""
"\n"
"Use your Special Moves to get up the air cons!\n"
"For Jazz, press Crouch and Jump.\n"
"For Spaz, Press Jump Twice!"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Utilisez vos Mouvements Spéciaux\n"
"pour soulever les conduites d'air\n"
