"\n"
"Trouvez le coffre pour éliminer les blocs"

#: .fake/Translations/secretf/09_town3.j2l.h:2
msgctxt "secretf/09_town3"
msgid ""
"\n"
"BEWARE! Flocks of Ravens can\n"
"be very dangerous."
